Project Structure

collabtask/
└── backend/                        # Backend server with FastAPI and database logic
    ├── main.py                     # FastAPI app entry point and router registration
    ├── database.py                 # Database connection and ORM base setup
    ├── .env                        # Environment variables for secrets and configs

    ├── models/                     # SQLAlchemy models defining DB tables
    │   └── schedule.py             # Schedule table schema and ORM model

    ├── schemas/                    # Pydantic models for request/response validation
    │   └── schedule.py             # Schedule input/output data schemas

    ├── crud/                       # Functions for database operations (CRUD)
    │   └── schedule.py             # CRUD logic for schedule items

    ├── routers/                    # API route handlers for FastAPI
    │   └── schedule.py             # Schedule-related endpoints

    ├── utils/                      # Helper utility functions (optional)
    │   └── time_utils.py           # Time/date utility functions

    ├── core/                       # App configuration and security modules (optional)
    │   └── config.py               # Configuration loader (env vars, settings)

    ├── frontend/                   # Frontend source code (React, Vue, etc.)
    │   └── src/                    # Frontend source files

    └── README.md                   # Project overview and instructions
